original_title: FLY! BOYS, FLY! 僕たち、CAはじめました
overview: When Chikara Asakawa was a child, he traveled with his parents and boarded an airplane. He got scared on the airplane, but a female flight attendant gave him courage. Chikara Asakawa became interested in being a flight attendant.
title: FLY! BOYS, FLY! 僕たち、CAはじめました
